body:
Mosswip Challenges!


Record/Screenshot all clips of you completing the challenges, and post them below in a one reply!
___________________________________________________________________________

  • Do a 360 shot on a One in the Chamber game with a bow.
  • Get everyone to scream for you in TeamSpeak or in the Minecraft Chat.
  • Destroy all monuments at once as a team.
  • Create a stylish defence.
  • Destroy the monument in below one minute of the game starting.
  • Get an undisturbed feed.
  • Vote for the server over 3 times.
  • Earn Prestige 1
  • Earn Prestige 2
  • Get a Mod to send you an autograph.
  • Complete 5 of these challenges.
  • Get into a channel in TeamSpeak with more than 8 people in it.

___________________________________________________________________________

Please note that I was bored when I wrote this, so no hate. Also, if you think of some challenges post them below and I'll add them to the list above with the person who thought of it.

Good luck with the challenges!

May the Moss be in your favour.
